cacheTempView("
select pogMarketingFeedBaseTab as pogId
        ,sum(finalNmpu*pogWeightage)/sum(pogWeightage) as NMSO
        ,sum(finalNmpu*pogWeightage*(1-cancellationPer))/sum(pogWeightage) as NMBO
        ,sum((finalNmpu-totalFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab+laapFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab)*pogWeightage)/sum(pogWeightage) as NM3SO
        ,sum((finalNmpu-totalFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab+laapFixedFfcMarketingFeedBaseTab)*pogWeightage*(1-cancellationPer))/sum(pogWeightage) as NM3BO
from(
    select distinct *
    from marketingFeedBaseTable
    ) a
group by pogMarketingFeedBaseTab
","temp.pogs_nmso")

","temp.disablePogs")
